I am trying to bind a doubleclick event on the listviewitem.<br />
After some time i found a solution:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;UserControl.Resources&gt;
    &lt;Style x:Key=&quot;itemstyle&quot; TargetType=&quot;{x:Type ListViewItem}&quot;&gt;
        &lt;EventSetter Event=&quot;MouseDoubleClick&quot; Handler=&quot;HandleDoubleClick&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/Style&gt;
&lt;/UserControl.Resources&gt;</code></pre>

The problem is this operation cancel the mui style and apply the standard windows style. Is there something i can do to have the mui style and set this event?<br />
